    {
      "id": "1ac4750c-f3ba-80b7-a120-caeb72ea72ee",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Remote learning has been a recourse option ever since the arisal of Covid-19. This has generated a big influx of new educational materials and, simultaneously, fast migration to online has brought the cold start to the spotlight. ",
