    {
      "id": "1ac4750c-f3ba-807c-ac64-f118a515acf0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors propose what they call online computation. Authors use a lightweight learner-micro-OER profile and use 2 algorithms to address the cold-start problem for users and contents. The recommender system generates learning paths.",
